Description: Graphical keyboard testing utility with typing test
 A comprehensive keyboard testing tool for Ubuntu that captures and displays
 detailed information about keyboard key presses. Features include:
  * Complete keyboard event capture (keys, modifiers, function keys)
  * Typing test mode with WPM tracking and statistics
  * Real-time error detection with color-coded feedback
  * Performance history tracking and analysis
  * 50 public domain text samples for typing practice
 .
 The application provides detailed keystroke information including key names,
 Qt key codes, native virtual key codes, and modifier states.
